MDD¶

In [18]:
kospi = pdr.get_data_yahoo('^KS11', '2004-01-04')

window=252    # 주식 개장일
peak = kospi['Adj Close'].rolling(window, min_periods=1).max()
drawdown = kospi['Adj Close']/peak - 1.0
max_dd = drawdown.rolling(window, min_periods=1).min()

In [36]:
